---
---

<section class="fc-section container-x">
  <div class="fc-label">— end of stack —</div>

  <h2 class="fc-title">
    You made it to the bottom.<br />
    <em class="fc-accent italic">Most people don't.</em>
  </h2>

  <p class="fc-sub">
    Open to senior contract engagements and full-time roles at AI-first companies. If you've
    read this far, you already know if we're a fit.
  </p>

  <div class="fc-ctas">
    <a href="mailto:me@algoro.dev" class="fc-btn-primary">me@algoro.dev →</a>
    <a href="/cv.pdf" class="fc-btn-ghost" data-no-panel>Download CV ↓</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .fc-section {
    padding: 120px 0 100px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .fc-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--layer-void-muted);
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
  .fc-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 108px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--layer-void-text);
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .fc-accent {
    color: var(--layer-void-accent);
  }
  .fc-sub {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--layer-void-muted);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto 52px;
  }
  .fc-ctas {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .fc-btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: var(--layer-void-accent);
    color: white;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 14px 24px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }
  .fc-btn-primary:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }
  .fc-btn-ghost {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--layer-void-accent);
    border: 1px solid var(--layer-void-accent);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 14px 24px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }
  .fc-btn-ghost:hover {
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
</style>
